title: Creamy Dill Sauce
ingredients: ["3 Tbsp. margarine or butter", "3 Tbsp. flour", "2 c. Borden or Meadow Gold milk", "1 tsp. chicken flavor bouillon or 3 cubes", "2 tsp. lemon juice", "3/4 tsp. dill weed"]
directions: ["In medium saucepan, melt margarine.", "Stir in flour until smooth.", "Gradually add milk, then bouillon, lemon juice and dill weed.", "Cook and stir until slightly thickened.", "Serve with hot cooked vegetables."]
